46
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,580
You are indeed experienced, master.

47
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,320
That is to say,

48
00:03:17,640 --> 00:03:18,900
Wang Hongjia used to be

49
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,650
