114
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:13,970
Captain Sun.

115
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,890
It should be just ahead.

116
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:07,800
The smell of nitric acid.

117
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,080
The killer must have

118
