130
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:25,920
I'll go find out.

131
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:26,780
Let's split up.

132
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,520
Be careful.

133
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:30,680
Lin Xiao.

134
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,540
You follow him.

135
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,440
Don't let him do anything rash.

136
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:33,960
Okay.

137
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:11,480
Yan.

138
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,560
Yan.

139
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,400
We are still looking for Ma Jinguang.

140
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,440
No news so far.

141
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,880
His phone has been turned off.

142
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,740
