151
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:36,480
It's highly likely that Ma Jinguang wasn't caught on camera.

152
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,440
But if he came from Kong Jiao's home,

153
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:40,840
