155
00:10:43,920 --> 00:10:46,400
They definitely would have caught Ma Jinguang on camera.

156
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,600
However, that night,

157
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:50,500
Ma Jinguang said he was going to sell ore,

158
00:10:50,760 --> 00:10:52,290
