223
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:33,180
An old Santana with new tires.

224
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:45,320
Boss.

225
00:12:46,920 --> 00:12:47,560
Boss.

226
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,280
Oh.

227
