245
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:42,720
Let's go.

246
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:43,760
Let's check it out.

247
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,040
Oh.

248
00:13:45,760 --> 00:13:46,520
Hurry and notify Lao Wang.

249
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:47,120
