00:15:25,720 --> 00:15:27,640
It's up to us to decide if we can arrest him.

292
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:29,560
If you're his friend, you should save him.

293
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:30,890
This is his last chance.

294
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:35,740
He came to see me yesterday

295
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,680
and asked just one question.

296
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,400
Is the mine really sealed,

297
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:41,060
and is anyone watching it now?

298
00:15:41,880 --> 00:15:43,210
I guess he's out of money

299
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,200
and wants to pull off a big one.

300
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:46,860
He told me to wait for his word.

301
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:55,850
Motorcycle tracks.

302
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:10,800
So this is where

303
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:12,720
he switched to a motorcycle.

304
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,520
Looks like it.

305
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,240
Heading west on this road

306
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,300
is Yinxing Avenue.

307
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:36,040
South of Yinxing Avenue is the city area.

308
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:36,960
To the north,

309
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,890
is near the highway where Qiao Sisi was found.

310
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:42,560
The old mine.

311
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:45,320
It's also where Ma Jinguang

312
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:46,640
works in the mine.

313
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:15,619
Tell them to go to the old mine.

314
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:21,119
Hey, Yan.

315
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,210
Captain Sun.

316
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:24,040
I think we are heading in the wrong direction.

317
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:24,680
What direction?

318
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:26,200
The steel balls are too obvious,

319
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,280
so the bomb was most likely

320
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:28,410
made by Ma Jinguang.

321
00:17:29,200 --> 00:17:30,640
But as for Zhang Biao's case,

322
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:32,100
I feel like he didn't do it.

323
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:33,120
You mean

324
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:35,080
the killer is framing Ma Jinguang?

325
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:35,810
Very likely.

326
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:37,000
I think all this

327
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,720
is deliberately arranged by the killer.

328
00:17:38,720 --> 00:17:40,050
At Ma Jinguang's house,

329
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,040
I found out he actually bought

330
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:42,570
many identical backpacks.

331
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,160
If he was really online

332
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,480
illegally selling explosives,

333
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,160
for safety,

334
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:48,400
they definitely wouldn't trade face-to-face.

335
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:50,440
They'd just leave the stuff at a drop-off spot.

336
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:50,880
So,

337
00:17:50,960 --> 00:17:52,040
he used the backpacks

338
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:53,440
to hold the explosives he sold.

339
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:54,720
After getting the explosives,

340
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,400
the killer threw the backpack at the crime scene

341
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,130
to frame him.

342
00:17:57,360 --> 00:17:59,090
But the backpack is a variable.

343
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:02,040
If Ma Jinguang had bought different styles of backpacks,

344
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,840
the framing would hardly succeed.

345
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,280
Unless the killer had been tracking him

346
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:08,160
and even sneaked into his house.

347
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:09,400
Since the killer was dead set

348
00:18:09,400 --> 00:18:10,920
on making it look like Ma Jinguang did it,

349
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:12,400
he would definitely make Wang Hongjia

350
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:13,330
appear near him.

351
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:14,480
This way,

352
00:18:14,840 --> 00:18:15,360
Zhang Biao

353
00:18:15,360 --> 00:18:16,320
becomes his victim,

354
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:17,040
and Wang Hongjia

355
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,680
was kidnapped by him to the cabin.

356
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:19,640
It all connects.

357
00:18:19,800 --> 00:18:22,200
That's probably how the killer planned it.

358
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,960
But there was an accident.

359
00:18:24,200 --> 00:18:25,060
What accident?

360
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,640
I'll confirm it soon.

361
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:28,800
I'm almost there.

362
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,010
Where did you go?

363
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:30,890
The mine.

364
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:32,140
It's getting dark.

365
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,680
The mine could be dangerous.

366
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:34,360
Be careful.

367
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:35,120
I'm coming over now.

368
00:18:35,120 --> 00:18:35,440
Okay.

369
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,520
Come over as soon as possible.
